items.name: case notConnected
items.desc: The flow is not fully opened.

items.name: case peerReset
items.desc: The flow was closed by the remote peer of the flow.

items.name: case hostUnreachable
items.desc: The remote endpoint of the flow could not be reached.

items.name: case invalidArgument
items.desc: An invalid argument was passed to a NEAppProxyFlow method.

items.name: case refused
items.desc: The flow could not be connected to its remote endpoint.

items.name: case `internal`
items.desc: An internal error was encountered while handling the flow.
